  <summary>4/29/1998--Introduced.
Amends Federal law to include within the Valley Forge National Historical Park the Paoli Battlefield in Malvern, Pennsylvania. Authorizes appropriations to acquire Battlefield property. Authorizes the Secretary of the Interior to enter into a cooperative agreement with Malvern Borough for the Borough management of the Battlefield Addition.</summary>
